## CRITICAL FOCUS RULES

Your response MUST be about what JUST CHANGED because of this event. Base your thoughts ONLY on:
    - Your character profile
    - Listed memories
    - The scene description
    - The most recent dialogue/events
    - **How this event relates to your active quests (if at all)**

DO NOT:
    - Invent new people, places, factions, items, or past events
    - Assume specific future outcomes; worry only in general terms
    - Re-tell past events (assume you remember them clearly)
    - Drift into unrelated worries
    - Let quest obligations override your immediate reaction to what just happened

